---
import PageLayout from '../components/templates/PageLayout.astro';
import FaqItem from '../components/molecules/FaqItem.astro';
import Button from '../components/atoms/Button.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Shipping & Returns | Ikeda Senchado">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-12">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-[120px] flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-secondary tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 uppercase">Customer Care</span>
      <h1 class="font-h1 text-h1 text-primary mb-6">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-tertiary-container max-w-2xl">
        Each parcel from Uji is carefully prepared to honor the journey from leaf to your hands.
        Below you will find our policies on delivery, returns, and damaged goods.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Shipping Section -->
    <section class="pb-24">
      <div class="border-b border-outline-variant pb-4 mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-primary">Shipping</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-0">
        <FaqItem question="When will my order ship?" open>
          Orders are processed within 1–2 business days of receipt. Once your order has been packed,
          you will receive a tracking number by email. Standard fulfillment occurs Monday through Friday,
          excluding Japanese national holidays.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="What shipping methods are available?">
          We offer Carbon Neutral Standard Delivery (5–8 business days domestically) and Express Delivery
          (1–3 business days). International shipping is available to over 40 countries via DHL Express
          with tracking and signature on delivery.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="How much does shipping cost?">
          Domestic shipping is complimentary on orders over ¥10,000. Standard rates begin at ¥800 for
          smaller orders. International rates are calculated at checkout based on weight and destination.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="Do you ship internationally?">
          Yes, we ship to over 40 countries worldwide. Please note that customs duties, import taxes,
          and any additional fees imposed by your country are the responsibility of the recipient.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="My package has not arrived. What should I do?">
          Please first check the tracking link sent to your email. If your package has been marked
          delivered but you cannot locate it, contact us within 7 days at support@ikedasenchado.jp and
          we will assist with a claim or replacement.
        </FaqItem>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Returns Section -->
    <section class="pb-[120px]">
      <div class="border-b border-outline-variant pb-4 mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-primary">Returns &amp; Refunds</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-0">
        <FaqItem question="What is your return policy on tea products?" open>
          Due to the perishable nature of tea, all sales are final once the seal has been broken.
          If you receive an unopened product and wish to return it, please contact us within 14 days
          of delivery for return authorization.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="My order arrived damaged. How do I report it?">
          We are sorry. Please email a photograph of the damaged item and packaging to
          support@ikedasenchado.jp within 7 days of receipt. We will arrange a replacement at no
          additional cost.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="Can I exchange ceramics or accessories?">
          Unopened, unused ceramics and accessories may be exchanged within 14 days of delivery.
          Items must be in their original packaging. Customers are responsible for return shipping
          costs unless the exchange is due to a defect.
        </FaqItem>
        <FaqItem question="How long does a refund take?">
          Once we receive your returned item and confirm its condition, refunds are processed to the
          original payment method within 5–7 business days. Bank processing times vary.
        </FaqItem>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="border-t border-outline-variant py-[120px] flex flex-col items-center">
      <h3 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-primary mb-6 text-center">Need further assistance?</h3>
      <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-tertiary-container mb-10 text-center max-w-lg">
        Our customer care team in Kyoto is available to answer specific shipping or return questions.
      </p>
      <Button variant="primary" as="a" href="/contact/">Contact Us</Button>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
